Package: rats
Type: Package
Title: Relative Abundance of Transcripts
Version: 0.1
Date: 2016-05-11
Author: Kira Mourao, Kimon Froussios, Nick Schurch
Maintainer: Nick SChurch <n.schurch@dundee.ac.uk>
Description: Given a Sleuth output object and a transcript-to-gene index of identifiers, this package identifies genes where differential transcript usage occurs.
